{"tid":86232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將政府派發6千元捐慈善機構　梁振英稱朋友提醒記起　","createTime":"2017-01-19T02:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T19:12:59.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06419efb08e3c930137df9d2b2628105797d229b","tid":86232,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"行政長官梁振英昨日在記者上，重提2011年政府全民派6千元，他至今都無領取，6千元仍在庫房，有報道指，他當年曾表示會將6千元捐到慈善機構，質疑有關款項仍在庫房的說法。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英出席電台聯播節目被追問有關問題時說，昨日已有朋友發短訊提醒他真的捐了錢，說明了該筆款項不應給他。<br />\n<br />\n至於政府當時應否派錢，他笑說，只能說出自己的取態。"},{"pid":"506508af4c710479bb610f4fc5207a573e16999b","tid":86232,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T02:04:56.000Z","msg":"臨死都講大話"},{"pid":"a5730b6c90a0d4235e0a95fa4bee3a4c2ad3c0bc","tid":86232,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c769b211f859dd8adc8482af041d78b98e03ac","tid":86232,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:37:22.000Z","msg":"捐左錢姐係拎左啦<br />\n之前冇拎 依家可以拎返？<br />\n咁姐係拎左定未拎"},{"pid":"7b6d99b9f648ecb6e58936762dd4115a6048197b","tid":86232,"uid":34641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"咁小事都要講大話...."},{"pid":"b8d5d369e3c2c41d3ad64636207d6ba2796f4d36","tid":86232,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:47:42.000Z","msg":"狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028fb567edb0c5af944ba3ad804bfde2e022a3e6","tid":86232,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55db239ffde19657067524d54124f6ae86a5da01","tid":86232,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face